<div class="res-text richtextContent background-hidden" id="2f5b888c-6f3c-4b99-abec-f323aaaffdfe" >

    <p>Ryerson aspires to have its employees reflect the diversity of its students and the community. To help us to see how we are doing, we include available comparison information.</p>
    





</div>
<script>$(document).ready(function(){addCoursePopover("#2f5b888c-6f3c-4b99-abec-f323aaaffdfe");});</script></div>

